  "instructions": [
    "Heat ghee in a large skillet over medium heat.",
    "Add onion and garlic, sauté until softened.",
    "Add ground beef and cook until browned, breaking into smaller pieces as it cooks.",
    "Stir in tomato paste, chili powder, turmeric, coriander, cumin seeds, salt, and water or vegetable broth. Bring to a boil.",
    "Reduce heat to low, cover, and let simmer for about 1 hour or until the beef is tender and most of the liquid has evaporated.",
    "Stir in chopped cilantro before serving."
